headline: CarMax Faces Omni-Channel Uncertainty as Morgan Stanley Cuts Target
summary: CarMax, Inc. (NYSE:KMX) is one of the oversold mid-cap stocks to buy according to hedge funds. On October 1, 2025, Morgan Stanley lowered its price target on CarMax from $80 to $56 while maintaining an Overweight rating.
